Class MaxVertexTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.BaseAggregateFunction
      • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.AbstractTimeAggregateFunction
        • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.MaxTime
          • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.MaxVertexTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AggregateFunction, VertexAggregateFunction, TemporalAggregateFunction

    public class MaxVertexTime
extends MaxTime
implements VertexAggregateFunction
    Aggregates the maximum value of a time value for temporal vertices. The value will be calculated as the maximum of a TimeDimension.Field of a TimeDimension, ignoring the default value (in this case Long.MAX_VALUE).
